<1ST_LINE>a a BC-SPE--SpecialEdition:FoodandDrink     11-21 0198</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>BC-SPE--Special Edition: Food and Drink,0219</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>PUBLISHERS:</HEAD>
<HEAD>ached at 212-621-1852@3.</HEAD>
<TEXT>
   The ``Food and Drink'' Special Edition contains these stories:
   b1333 BC-SPE--Food: Test Kitchen (LaserPhoto NY701)
   b1334 BC-SPE--Food: Specialty Foods (LaserPhotos NY704, NY707)
